author: Play On Tabletop
description:
This episode sponsored by Adept Roll: https://adeptroll.com A 40k companion app where you can input the stats of any unit or weapon to get the likelihood of it succeeded or failing. Great for theory hammering out a list or figuring out that crucial game decision!

Tanya is back in the studio with her fan favourite Orks taking on Steve who has picked the Dark Angels as his Space Marine flavour of the day.  It's a battle to decide who gets to claim the colour green! LISTS below in the description.
